'''Oxonmoot 2014''' is the 41st Oxonmoot held annually by [[The Tolkien Society]]. The event is an extra day long, in honour of Oxonmoot's 40th Anniversary.<ref>{{webcite|website=TS|articlename=Oxonmoot 2014|articleurl=http://www.tolkiensociety.org/society/events/oxonmoot/|accessed=17 August 2014}}</ref>
